{"title":"hexo的live2d插件","slug":"hexo的live2d插件","date":"2017-01-29T08:29:29.000Z","updated":"2018-05-08T03:49:28.218Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"<p>为你的hexo添加色气满满的live2d吧！</p>","content":"<p>为你的hexo添加色气满满的live2d吧！</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p><a href=\"https://badge.fury.io/js/hexo-helper-live2d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://badge.fury.io/js/hexo-helper-live2d.svg\" alt=\"npm version\"></a></p>\n<div id=\"badge-container-EYHN-hexo-helper-live2d-81d768d\" class=\"hexo-github\" style=\"width: 100%\"></div>\n<script src=\"/hexo-github/badge.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n  loadStyle(\"/hexo-github/style.css\");\n  loadStyle(\"/hexo-github/octicons/octicons.css\");\n  new Badge(\"#badge-container-EYHN-hexo-helper-live2d-81d768d\", \"EYHN\", \"hexo-helper-live2d\", \"81d768d\", false);\n</script>\n\n<h2 id=\"hexo-helper-live2d\"><a href=\"#hexo-helper-live2d\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo-helper-live2d\"></a>hexo-helper-live2d</h2><p>为你的hexo添加色气满满的live2d吧！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><del>Example: <a href=\"https://delusion.coding.me/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://delusion.coding.me/</a></del></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/hexo的live2d插件/z16.jpg\" alt=\"范例图片\" title=\"z16\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"食用方法：\"><a href=\"#食用方法：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"食用方法：\"></a>食用方法：</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将下面的代码加入主题。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;canvas id=<span class=\"string\">\"live2dcanvas\"</span> width=<span class=\"string\">\"300\"</span> height=<span class=\"string\">\"600\"</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span></span>=<span class=\"string\">\"live2d\"</span>&gt;&lt;/canvas&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%- live2d(<span class=\"string\">\"live2dcanvas\"</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">.live2d&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  position: fixed;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tbottom: <span class=\"number\">-30</span>px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tright: <span class=\"number\">0</span>px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tz-index: <span class=\"number\">999</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\twidth: <span class=\"number\">150</span>px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\theight: <span class=\"number\">300</span>px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pointer-events: none;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;<span class=\"regexp\">/style&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\n<p>暂时还不能添加其他模型，<del>不过很快就会更新</del>，所以请点个watch实时追踪更新吧！</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我第一个hexo插件,点个star,点个watch吧。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Github: <a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d</a></p>\n<p>issues: <a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/issues</a></p>\n<p>求英文好的小伙伴提交一个英文版的README，直接提交PR就可以啦!</p>\n<h2 id=\"About-me\"><a href=\"#About-me\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"About me\"></a>About me</h2><p><a href=\"https://delusion.coding.me/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/author-cneyhn-green.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Author\"></a><br><a href=\"http://wpa.qq.com/msgrd?v=3&amp;uin=&amp;site=qq&amp;menu=yes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/QQ-1106996185-blue.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"QQ\"></a><br><a href=\"\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Emali%20me-cneyhn@gmail.com-green.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Email\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"License-许可证\"><a href=\"#License-许可证\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"License 许可证\"></a>License 许可证</h2><p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/master/LICENSE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"license\"></a></p>\n<p>Open sourced under the GPL v2.0 license.</p>\n<p>根据 GPL V2.0 许可证开源。</p>\n","thumbnail":"/img/hexo的live2d插件/live2d z16.jpg","primarycolor":"blueGrey","accentcolor":"blueGrey","categories":[{"name":"项目","path":"api/categories/项目.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"发布","path":"api/tags/发布.json"},{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"开源","path":"api/tags/开源.json"}]}